{"tid":2351316,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾南山：中國抗疫成功 民眾返鄉過春節沒問題","createTime":"2021-01-03T06:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T14:36:33.000Z","uid":337052,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"776f286a41e2b615f242b34b7fddff46bed61d55","tid":2351316,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">春節可否趴趴走 鍾南山：沒必要禁出行</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2021/01/03 14:02<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北3日電）<span class=\"red\">農曆春節將屆，今年中國春運鐵路運輸量預計逾4億人次，與去年相當，在2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19）疫情陰影下，有人認為染疫風險高，但官民眼中的權威專家鍾南山認為沒必要禁出行。</span><br />\n<br />\n中國國鐵集團稍早宣布，今年春運將於1月28日登場，3月8日結束，預計運送旅客4.07億人次。以此計算，每天平均運送1018萬人次旅客。<br />\n<br />\n綜合星島日報等港媒報導，由於北京、遼寧等地近日持續出現零星的本土確診病例，許多人擔心今年春運規模與去年不相上下，可能不利防控疫情。<br />\n<br />\n天津中醫藥大學校長張伯禮認為，疫情到今年一月底仍屬「高危時段」，建議有關部門提前安排春節返程休假時間，避免所有人都擠在高峰幾天回程，「可以不回家（過年）的暫時就先不要回」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，中國工程院院士鍾南山日前接受官媒央視訪問時表示，<span class=\"red\">中國國內雖仍存在疫情反覆、散發出現的情況，但已形成了非常有效、比較嚴密的防控，不太可能再出現去年初的大規模爆發。</span><br />\n<br />\n鍾南山是中國官民眼中的權威防疫專家，去年底才在母校華南師範大學附屬中學為自己銅像揭幕，稍早時的去年9月並因抗疫有功的理由獲中共當局頒發「共和國勳章」。<br />\n<br />\n他說，隨著中國大陸疫情受控，出行需求增加是必然的，沒必要禁止民眾出行，但不鼓勵去國外，也不要去中國官方列為中風險的地區。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">他建議民眾出行要注意「戴口罩、勤洗手、保持距離」，「要是這樣的話，我覺得還是可以平安度過新年和春節」</span>。（編輯：周慧盈/吳柏緯）1100103"},{"pid":"dd56e165a99c813f53880a602970db27176b8698","tid":2351316,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:27:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202101030079.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202101030079.aspx&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=5e9b0395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202101030079.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"ac24c0c97cf9909c20c0b1c77156c1824efb2d83","tid":2351316,"uid":48277,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:28:07.000Z","msg":"抗疫我只相鍾南山<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98ef71314cc78b31fbcf3b6171b70adb3ebd75e2","tid":2351316,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:29:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">北京遼寧外 中國本土疫情再添黑龍江河北</span></strong><br />\n最新更新：2021/01/03 09:12<br />\n<br />\n（中央社台北3日電）<span class=\"red\">中國本土疫情近來在北京、遼寧等地出現，2日中國大陸新增確診病例24例，其中境外移入病例16例，本土病例8例，分別為黑龍江4例，遼寧2例，北京1例，河北1例。</span><br />\n<br />\n中國國家衛生健康委員會上午在官網通報，2日0至24時，中國31個省（自治區、直轄市）和新疆生產建設兵團報告新增確診病例24例，其中境外移入病例16例，分別為上海6例，福建2例，廣東2例，陝西2例，北京1例，天津1例，內蒙古1例，遼寧1例。<br />\n<br />\n本土病例8例，分別為黑龍江4例，遼寧2例，北京1 例，河北1例，沒有新增疑似病例，也沒有死亡病例。<br />\n<br />\n境外移入現有確診病例279例，現有疑似病例1例。累計確診病例4303例，累計治癒出院病例4024例。<br />\n<br />\n截至1月2日24時，中國大陸現有確診病例395例，累計治癒出院病例8萬2088例，累計死亡病例4634例，累計報告確診病例8萬7117例，現有疑似病例1例。累計追蹤到密切接觸者90萬7460人，尚在醫學觀察的密切接觸者1萬4175人。<br />\n<br />\n無症狀感染者2日新增8例，都是境外移入。當日轉為確診病例5例，當日解除醫學觀察14例。尚在醫學觀察的無症狀感染者269例，境外移入占225例。<br />\n<br />\n此外，香港特別行政區累計確診8923例，其中出院7968例，死亡150例；澳門特別行政區累計確診46例，皆已出院。（編輯：翟思嘉）1100103<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202101030015.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F202101030015.aspx&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=9929429d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/202101030015.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"5fffa1565a5f46bcd01c8e44282ec03049601680","tid":2351316,"uid":55851,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"到時爆果時一定話英國肺炎大爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6f185e2ec269cefd69b878a208952ffc35addd","tid":2351316,"uid":86449,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"無事既<br />\n十一長假都無事<br />\n春運算得咩"},{"pid":"b6e4bafbc917597120f4e48fc372c77fb27ab964","tid":2351316,"uid":2300,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:33:10.000Z","msg":"唔公佈=無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f925a2d97eab75c42403ec9414fa8368886b9c","tid":2351316,"uid":53105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"上年都係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df432ba235246148ee40cc07bb23345320480c34","tid":2351316,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:36:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中國疫情 鍾南山：病毒會通過環境傳染</span></strong><br />\n鍾南山<br />\n <br />\nCOVID-19<br />\n時間：2020-12-19 21:30新聞引據：、東網撰稿編輯：黃啟霖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2020/03/27/fbf35fc8e74e3a9a25856de36b873b7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2020%2F03%2F27%2Ffbf35fc8e74e3a9a25856de36b873b7b.jpg&h=ea56d43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國工程院院士鍾南山表示，近日中國出現患者經接觸冷凍貨品外包裝感染個案，顯示COVID-19「原本是人傳人，現在出現環境傳人的情況」(資料圖片/微博)<br />\n<br />\n東網報導，<span class=\"red\">中國工程院院士鍾南山今天(19日)表示，近日中國內地出現患者經接觸冷凍貨品外包裝感染個案，顯示2019年冠狀病毒疾病(COVID-19)「原本是人傳人，現在出現環境傳人的情況」</span>；當局需就此研究新的預防措施。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山指出，現時中國大陸感染個案主要分為兩類：一是境外輸入，二是新冠病毒通過環境進行傳播；後者則產生多個疫情防控相關問題，包括冷鏈外包裝的病毒會不會使人感染、病毒濃度達到多高會出現感染、病毒能夠存活多少天等。<br />\n<br />\n鍾南山指出，當局若要嚴格控制疫情，則須找出個中規律。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2087205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2087205&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=5a456c80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2087205</a>"},{"pid":"ebc479a68ea9b3aaab3bbc781fec5eccaba81c93","tid":2351316,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9f925a2d97eab75c42403ec9414fa8368886b9c","tid":2351316,"uid":53105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"上年都係咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">可防可控</span>"},{"pid":"5f9d2dbe6760328c8773545999fc4e0208bdd86b","tid":2351316,"uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:37:37.000Z","msg":"支持 認同"},{"pid":"3a7d2e30a0e4ebf7043578b4b0b706d98d842f85","tid":2351316,"uid":21279,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:38:43.000Z","msg":"十卜<br />\n<br />\n個個咩yc袁國勇我先唔會信<br />\n<br />\n只信鐘南山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d06c88aa1f356e40c5e6a68f8f46283aba2f7f","tid":2351316,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:39:36.000Z","msg":"去年就是因為中國春運<br />\n<br />\n才造成武漢肺炎流向全世界"},{"pid":"4fd49ce1ab2bbcd9019bcdf3b709ac97e5ec0bab","tid":2351316,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:39:51.000Z","msg":"等你地返晒鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5369551e5fe4a1c1472fdb9b0cb1399f7067a19","tid":2351316,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">新冠肺炎：廣州首現英變種病毒 港人赴深圳驗出無症狀感染</span></strong><br />\n2021年1月3日週日 上午11:05 [GMT+8]&middot;1 分鐘文章<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">英國的變種新冠病毒入侵內地，繼上海之後，廣東昨日(2日)也首次發現英國變種病毒株。而深圳則驗出一宗來自香港的無症狀感染個案。</span><br />\n<br />\n廣東省疾控中心對去年9月以來的境外輸入確診及無症狀感染者病毒樣本進行分析，至昨日發現一名去年12月4日從英國入境的確診18歲中國男子的病毒樣本，與英國變種病毒基因序列高度相似。<br />\n<br />\n該患者是一名留學生，入境廣州時病毒核酸檢測顯示他無染疫，至同月18日在隔離點覆檢時顯示受感染，送廣州市第八人民醫院隔離治療，經診斷確診，目前仍留院觀察。廣東省疾控中心同月27日對該院採集的病例樣本進行基因組測序分析時，初步發現變種病毒株，上周六再次進行高通量測序覆核確認。<br />\n<br />\n另外，廣東省衞健委今日(3日)通報，過去一日全省新增境外輸入確診病例兩宗，廣州一宗來自孟加拉，肇慶一宗則來自印尼。同日新增2宗境外輸入無症狀感染個案，深圳一宗來自香港，佛山一人來自土耳其。以上確診及無症狀感染者均在隔離點發現，入境後即被隔離觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E%E9%A6%96%E7%8F%BE%E8%8B%B1%E8%AE%8A%E7%A8%AE%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B4%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA%E7%84%A1%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93-030501975.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%25A6%2596%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AE%258A%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%2597%2587%25E7%258B%2580%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593-030501975.html&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=3435f02a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E5%BB%A3%E5%B7%9E%E9%A6%96%E7%8F%BE%E8%8B%B1%E8%AE%8A%E7%A8%AE%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B4%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA%E7%84%A1%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93-030501975.html</a>"},{"pid":"f3388e89770240c9d53aae09f2bc64281bf8a36a","tid":2351316,"uid":175540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:44:42.000Z","msg":"唔禁~ 返家鄉~"},{"pid":"81e0257179d1323fe8061d9a9db0192c2c2a230b","tid":2351316,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:46:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KUioOxmTCU0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKUioOxmTCU0&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=5298ba0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KUioOxmTCU0</a><br />\n黑龍江疫情拉警報"},{"pid":"2b6aa99a0b9651553e9667cd25819ba2f985f24a","tid":2351316,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O1UodFDUeDQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO1UodFDUeDQ&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0DXucVKzxOX0ld4zZjK7Pao%3D&h=c78bf2d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O1UodFDUeDQ</a>"},{"pid":"c653a371dec9bbe765051351b916a77b4b777bed","tid":2351316,"uid":33705